{"tid":1287037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人手置頂】【更正】啲狗係可以隨時「搜查」物品，但係一定要拘捕左先可以「沒收」","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:27:23.000Z","uid":138409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8045e25bedc2721f4b87477cde57f1f239f000","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"見到隔離po啲字眼有啲混亂<br />\n律師黃國桐：隨身物品要警方進行拘捕後才可檢查<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286339</a><br />\n<br />\n驚各位手足一陣搞錯左畀人吿老妨就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用返法政匯思嘅懶人包<br />\n簡單來講<br />\n<br />\n1. 警方<span style=\"color: red;\">「合理懷疑」</span>你犯罪<br />\n--&gt; <span style=\"color: gold;\">「搜查」</span>隨身物品 <span style=\"color: gold;\">only</span><br />\n唔建議你質疑佢，最好就係記低詳情將來投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkplg/photos/a.1341950022638533/1342123869287815/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkplg%2Fphotos%2Fa.1341950022638533%2F1342123869287815%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=16803637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkplg/photos/a.1341950022638533/1342123869287815/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zg0C1Fs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzg0C1Fs.jpg&h=4d834d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 警方<span style=\"color: red;\">拘捕</span>你<br />\n--&gt; <span style=\"color: gold;\">「搜查」</span> + <span style=\"color: gold;\">「撿走」</span>隨身物品<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkplg/photos/a.1341950022638533/1342123772621158/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkplg%2Fphotos%2Fa.1341950022638533%2F1342123772621158%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=b570cc16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkplg/photos/a.1341950022638533/1342123772621158/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bUsEkR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bUsEkR.jpg&h=0317651c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於乜嘢係「合理懷疑」呢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2274103919369546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F2274103919369546&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=d4bcc486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2274103919369546</a><br />\n注意當中 腳註 [3][4][5] 係引用外國案例，香港法院跟唔跟呢....唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. 正如我昨天指出，「香港法例第232章《警隊條例》第54(2)條賦予警察的合法截停、查究及搜查權力，只限於在『合理地懷疑[某人]已經或即將或意圖犯任何罪行』時行使。」<br />\n <br />\n2. 根據時任原訟法庭法官潘兆初於《王子鑫訴警務處長》的判決，[1]<br />\n <br />\n「警員對某人的懷疑是否合理，必須以<span style=\"color: gold;\">客觀的事實</span>來定奪。這些客觀的事實 ... 包括當時的時間、地點、現場環境、那人的神情、舉止及動作等。」<br />\n <br />\n換言之，警員若是援引第54(2) 條，「必須有相關的證據支持他對那人的懷疑是合理的。」[2]<br />\n <br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">除非警員收到有關疑犯描述的情報，否則單憑刻板印象，無差別地對擁有某類個人特徵 － 例如外表和年齡 －的人進行搜查，決不合理。</span>[3]<br />\n <br />\n4. 同理，除非某人符合警方情報中對疑犯的描述，[4]否則該人身處的地方曾有罪案發生，或是所謂的犯罪黑點（so-called high crime area），本身不能成為截停搜查的理由。正如加拿大最高法院最近引用案例指出，即使某社區可稱作罪犯天堂，這也不代表任何進出此地的人，都可客觀地被懷疑干犯犯罪行為。[5]<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9a7c9c64ba55db910cbb856868f56e7bd5415b28","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9dafd405a7298cd419ad2c6301f04fe62864e84b","tid":1287037,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef7bfdea02167806ccb80ac04ac90181c8ae2dd","tid":1287037,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4324b1b348090b4e33a16fd8c5f7cbcbff520e7","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47e49205622dac42551f6064f1b65e02e3e433c8","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bd0c1d264cdd52cf96bd1bc7e8c519f18221e725","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"84ffb37a481610d3097f08a12c7b0a3f8ba43d72","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:54:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60b9598f42960ef641ef4e7913a41e1400e4c41a","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c31eddc6387b7b12658b47ae6859dce1903939df","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"707cf08dfaa10f1fa6ba49ee5919ef29a1c5865b","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:42:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89a68e663d0f44fa9073f0d2906bbe2bb8f07179","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63fd7f299a66eccb267966df9d1202d5d1c4ae06","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b21ef4e31c705866b0481706336e18ca6b20971d","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"02e65861da0838d9fba5826e6de75e7a66cd5daa","tid":1287037,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"push"}]}